728
00:50:34.152 --> 00:50:36.362
You don't like the turtles?
What's the problem?

729
00:50:36.445 --> 00:50:39.197
- I don't think I belong here.
- It's okay.

730
00:50:41.992 --> 00:50:43.786
I don't belong here.

731
00:50:44.454 --> 00:50:47.748
Well, you know, it's okay,
'cause you're my guest.

732
00:50:48.875 --> 00:50:51.878
I don't know you well enough.

733
00:50:51.960 --> 00:50:55.255
I've never been
in a man's apartment alone.

734
00:50:57.090 --> 00:50:59.927
Well, they're all the same, you know?

735
00:51:05.099 --> 00:51:07.684
