746
00:51:42.929 --> 00:51:45.306
Why don't you take off that hat?

747
00:51:51.603 --> 00:51:53.815
I always knew you was pretty.

748
00:51:55.358 --> 00:51:57.985
- Don't tease me.
- I'm not teasing you.

749
00:52:01.364 --> 00:52:03.157
I ain't teasing you.

750
00:52:04.242 --> 00:52:06.869
