1199
01:23:37.719 --> 01:23:40.805
<i>Today we're here with</i>
<i>heavyweight challenger Rocky Balboa.</i>

1200
01:23:40.886 --> 01:23:43.430
<i>The reason we're standing</i>
<i>in this refrigerated box</i>

1201
01:23:43.515 --> 01:23:46.728
<i>is that Mr. Balboa</i>
<i>has an unusual method of training.</i>

1202
01:23:46.810 --> 01:23:50.273
<i>In a moment, he'll demonstrate that</i>
<i>for the viewing audience at home.</i>

1203
01:23:50.354 --> 01:23:53.943
<i>But first, Rocky,</i>
<i>how did you come to train in an icebox?</i>

1204
01:23:54.569 --> 01:23:57.404
<i>Well, my friend, the guy over there,</i>

1205
01:23:57.488 --> 01:24:00.323
<i>he let me in one day,</i>
<i>and I hit the beef here and liked it,</i>

1206
01:24:00.408 --> 01:24:03.786
