<i>the owner don't mind that I come in.</i>

1207
01:24:03.868 --> 01:24:07.747
<i>Is this a common training method?</i>
<i>Do other fighters pound raw meat?</i>

1208
01:24:07.832 --> 01:24:09.792
<i>No, I think I invented it.</i>

1209
01:24:09.876 --> 01:24:12.627
<i>- Would you give us a demonstration?</i>
- Confirm the reservation

1210
01:24:12.712 --> 01:24:16.131
for my people at ringside,
and fly my barber to Philly.

1211
01:24:19.594 --> 01:24:22.639
How much is being channeled
into West Coast closed-circuit advertising?

1212
01:24:22.720 --> 01:24:24.974
- 300,000.
- Make it 450.

1213
01:24:25.055 --> 01:24:27.475
And send the mayor's wife
200 roses from me,

1214
01:24:27.560 --> 01:24:30.313
and make sure we get a picture of it
for all the newspapers.

1215
01:24:30.395 --> 01:24:33.483
Do you want to run the 15 radio spots
in the Midwest?

1216
01:24:33.564 --> 01:24:36.152
You can spend your money better
in Canadian publicity.

1217
01:24:36.234 --> 01:24:38.944
By the way, Apollo,
I've got friends in Toronto

1218
01:24:39.029 --> 01:24:40.988
who can get you a good tax break.

1219
01:24:41.073 --> 01:24:43.201
George, I like your friends.

1220
01:24:51.167 --> 01:24:55.587
Hey, Champ. You ought to come
look at this boy you're gonna fight on TV.

1221
01:24:56.255 --> 01:24:59.466
- Looks like he means business.
- Yeah, I mean business too.

1222
01:24:59.550 --> 01:25:01.676
Shirley, we got any more coffee out there?

1223
01:25:01.761 --> 01:25:04.389
Certainly, Mr. Creed.
I'll get you some right away.

1224
01:25:04.470 --> 01:25:07.684
After the fight,
I may retire and run for emperor.

1225
01:25:22.198 --> 01:25:24.533
<i>Diana Lewis in the meat house</i>

1226
01:25:24.617 --> 01:25:27.078
<i>with southpaw Rocky Balboa.</i>

1227
01:26:13.582 --> 01:26:15.542
And he called the reporters?

1228
01:26:15.626 --> 01:26:18.212
Yeah. Threw my training schedule off.

1229
01:26:18.296 --> 01:26:20.421
Don't be mad at him. He's trying to help.

1230
01:26:20.506 --> 01:26:22.300
Adrian, I ain't mad,

1231
01:26:22.381 --> 01:26:25.595
it's just that when reporters are
around, I get out of joint

1232
