- I'm a pig?

1255
01:27:49.554 --> 01:27:51.555
A pig gets you the best?

1256
01:27:52.345 --> 01:27:55.560
You're such a loser!
I don't get married because of you!

1257
01:27:55.935 --> 01:27:58.060
You can't live by yourself!

1258
01:27:58.479 --> 01:28:02.149
I put you two together,
and don't you forget it!

1259
01:28:02.233 --> 01:28:03.609
You owe me!

1260
