1267
01:28:27.216 --> 01:28:28.926
I'm not a loser!

1268
01:28:29.010 --> 01:28:30.845
- You're busted!
- What?

1269
01:28:30.926 --> 01:28:32.720
You're not a virgin!

1270
01:28:33.139 --> 01:28:35.430
You let a man take down your pants!

1271
01:28:35.515 --> 01:28:36.975
She's busted!

1272
01:28:40.063 --> 01:28:42.148
I can't haul meat no more!

1273
01:29:12.595 --> 01:29:14.389
You want a roommate?

1274
01:29:19.350 --> 01:29:20.685
Absolutely.

1275
01:29:22.563 --> 01:29:24.854
Okay, now when you walk into the ring

1276
01:29:24.939 --> 01:29:27.694
with the number one
heavyweight of the world

1277
01:29:27.777 --> 01:29:29.444
