1280
01:29:34.742 --> 01:29:37.161
You'll be able to spit nails, kid!

1281
01:29:37.243 --> 01:29:39.872
Like the guy says,
you're gonna eat lightning

1282
01:29:39.956 --> 01:29:41.832
and you're gonna crap thunder!

1283
01:29:41.916 --> 01:29:44.667
You're gonna become
a very dangerous person.

1284
01:29:44.752 --> 01:29:46.045
Yo, Mickey.

1285
01:29:46.127 --> 01:29:48.212
Hey, how are you? Oh, Rock.

1286
01:29:48.296 --> 01:29:51.384
I want you to meet our cut man here.
Al Salvani.

1287
01:29:51.466 --> 01:29:53.469
- Take a look at his eye.
- How you doing, Al?

1288
01:29:53.551 --> 01:29:55.970
- That's right.
- It ain't bad. Seen worse.

1289
01:29:56.055 --> 01:29:58.847
- You ain't so bad yourself.
- Cover up. Things will be okay.

1290
01:29:58.930 --> 01:30:00.143
You cover up.

1291
01:30:00.225 --> 01:30:01.978
Go and take a shower.

1292
01:30:02.060 --> 01:30:04.479
Okay, Mick. I'll see you tomorrow.

1293
01:30:05.479 --> 01:30:08.609
You covered that Whitmore fight?

1294
01:30:08.693 --> 01:30:11.444
- That's why he won.
- Listen. We got a winner here.

1295
01:30:11.529 --> 01:30:15.573
We got a chance. He goes to the body
like nobody you've ever seen.

1296
01:30:15.658 --> 01:30:18.493
You just stand by. We're gonna win.

1297
01:30:25.501 --> 01:30:28.002
Hey, Rock. It's okay I talk to you?

1298
01:30:28.587 --> 01:30:31.341
Okay you talk to me? Sure.

1299
01:30:32.131 --> 01:30:35.011
I figured some angle
to make some money off your name.

1300
01:30:35.094 --> 01:30:37.720
My name? How's that?

1301
01:30:37.889 --> 01:30:40.515
Advertising. I know about that stuff.

1302
01:30:42.350 --> 01:30:44.854
What do you know about advertising?

1303
01:30:48.149 --> 01:30:51.069
Hey, you can make money off my name,
make it, okay?

1304
01:30:51.152 --> 01:30:53.154
I'm gonna take a shower.

1305
01:30:54.113 --> 01:30:56.658
- Wanna help me off with these?
- Sure.

1306
01:32:31.961 --> 01:32:33.837
You're gonna kill him!

1307
01:35:24.716 --> 01:35:28.220
Rocky. What brings you here tonight?

1308
01:35:29.805 --> 01:35:31.765
Mr. Jergens, the poster's wrong.

1309
01:35:32.305 --> 01:35:33.975
What do you mean?

1310
01:35:34.143 --> 01:35:36.979
I'm wearing white pants with a red stripe.

1311
01:35:40.817 --> 01:35:43.234
It doesn't really matter, does it?

1312
01:35:43.319 --> 01:35:46.154
I'm sure you're gonna give us
a great show.

1313
01:35:47.154 --> 01:35:49.242
Try to get some rest, kid.

1314
01:35:50.076 --> 01:35:51.452
Good night.

1315
01:37:22.792 --> 01:37:24.337
I can't do it.

1316
01:37:27.421 --> 01:37:28.506
What?

1317
01:37:29.634 --> 01:37:31.260
I can't beat him.

1318
01:37:32.845 --> 01:37:34.095
Apollo?

1319
01:37:34.805 --> 01:37:35.974
Yeah.

1320
01:37:37.390 --> 01:37:40.310
I been out there, walking around, thinking.

1321
01:37:42.229 --> 01:37:45.483
Who am I kidding?
I ain't even in the guy's league.

1322
01:37:50.863 --> 01:37:52.698
What are we gonna do?

1323
01:38:04.292 --> 01:38:05.712
I don't know.

1324
01:38:12.091 --> 01:38:13.845
You worked so hard.

1325
01:38:15.720 --> 01:38:18.930
Yeah, it don't matter,
'cause I was nobody before.

1326
01:38:21.269 --> 01:38:22.854
Don't say that.

1327
01:38:23.563 --> 01:38:25.854
Oh, come on, Adrian. It's true.

1328
01:38:25.939 --> 01:38:27.442
I was nobody.

1329
01:38:29.359 --> 01:38:32.029
But that don't matter either, you know?

1330
01:38:33.072 --> 01:38:34.988
'Cause I was thinking,

1331
01:38:36.242 --> 01:38:39.162
it really don't matter if I lose this fight.

1332
01:38:41.247 --> 01:38:44.832
It really don't matter
if this guy opens my head either.

1333
01:38:46.127 --> 01:38:48.921
'Cause all I wanna do is go the distance.

1334
01:38:53.841 --> 01:38:56.720
Nobody's ever gone the distance
with Creed,

1335
01:38:57.555 --> 01:38:59.805
and if I can go that distance,

1336
01:39:01.225 --> 01:39:04.228
and that bell rings, and I'm still standing,

1337
01:39:09.524 --> 01:39:12.862
I'm gonna know
for the first time in my life, see,

1338
01:39:14.738 --> 01:39:18.242
that I weren't just another bum
from the neighborhood.

1339
01:40:25.725 --> 01:40:27.520
Time, kid. Let's go.

1340
01:40:30.564 --> 01:40:32.483
I'll wait for you here.

1341
01:40:34.819 --> 01:40:37.613
How about I wait here and you fight, huh?

1342
01:40:38.488 --> 01:40:41.576
You're looking very great today,
you know that?

1343
01:40:43.578 --> 01:40:46.662
I gotta go now,
but don't you leave town, huh?

1344
01:40:48.082 --> 01:40:50.460
Wish me luck. I'm gonna need it.

1345
01:40:51.210 --> 01:40:52.545
Good luck.

1346
01:40:53.337 --> 01:40:56.631
Adrian, you don't think
this robe is too baggy, huh?

1347
01:40:56.841 --> 01:40:58.176
Good luck.

1348
01:40:58.259 --> 01:40:59.886
Don't leave town.

1349
01:41:02.261 --> 01:41:05.890
<i>I'd like you to meet my colleague,</i>
<i>Stu Nahan.</i>

