01:41:05.975 --> 01:41:07.350
<i>Thank you, Bill Baldwin.</i>

1351
01:41:07.435 --> 01:41:10.188
<i>The electricity is all over the place tonight,</i>
<i>as Rocky Balboa...</i>

1352
01:41:12.104 --> 01:41:13.939
What is that?

1353
01:41:14.024 --> 01:41:16.359
I trained you to be a fighter,
not a billboard.

1354
01:41:16.444 --> 01:41:19.029
- I'm doing it for a friend.
- What do you get out of it?

1355
01:41:19.113 --> 01:41:21.032
