01:41:27.997 --> 01:41:30.041
<i>it could be</i>
<i>"the caveman against the cavalier."</i>

1360
01:41:30.122 --> 01:41:32.042
<i>I notice a buzzing in the background.</i>

1361
01:41:32.126 --> 01:41:34.712
<i>Could be the challenger</i>
<i>is getting ready to get into the ring.</i>

1362
01:41:34.796 --> 01:41:36.965
Rocky, look at my date.

1363
01:41:37.046 --> 01:41:39.050
- Cost me $200.
- $250.

1364
01:41:39.131 --> 01:41:40.801
I gotta go. I gotta work.

