1392
01:43:03.801 --> 01:43:05.219
I want you!

1393
01:43:06.470 --> 01:43:08.970
<i>The crowd is loving every minute of it.</i>

1394
01:43:09.055 --> 01:43:12.100
<i>- Here is the world heavyweight champion.</i>
