1395
01:43:12.185 --> 01:43:13.603
<i>For you around the world</i>

1396
01:43:13.685 --> 01:43:16.604
<i>he was dressed as George Washington,</i>
<i>the father of our country.</i>

1397
01:43:16.689 --> 01:43:18.064
I want you!

1398
01:43:20.818 --> 01:43:24.322
<i>I don't believe what I'm seeing.</i>
