01:44:35.310 --> 01:44:39.729
<i>show business and the sporting world</i>
<i>who are with us tonight</i>

1421
01:44:40.064 --> 01:44:42.233
<i>but I would like to present</i>

1422
01:44:42.317 --> 01:44:45.359
<i>one of the immortals of pugilism,</i>

1423
01:44:45.444 --> 01:44:49.073
<i>a champion in and out of the ring,</i>

1424
01:44:49.157 --> 01:44:51.908
<i>Philadelphia's own "Smokin' Joe,"</i>

1425
01:44:51.993 --> 01:44:54.828
<i>the beloved Mr. Joe Frazier!</i>

1426
01:45:05.590 --> 01:45:06.881
How you doing?

1427
01:45:06.966 --> 01:45:08.384
Don't hurt him, okay?

1428
01:45:08.466 --> 01:45:10.094
I'll try not to.

1429
01:45:10.176 --> 01:45:12.555
<i>What a credit he's been</i>
<i>in his career as a fighter.</i>

1430
01:45:12.639 --> 01:45:14.765
<i>Now he's coming over</i>
<i>to talk to the champ.</i>

1431
01:45:14.849 --> 01:45:17.268
- Hey, Joe.
- You been ducking me a long time.

1432
01:45:17.350 --> 01:45:19.020
No, Joe. You're next.

1433
01:45:19.103 --> 01:45:21.314
- You're next.
- You understand?

1434
01:45:21.854 --> 01:45:23.439
They must be friends.

1435
01:45:31.823 --> 01:45:33.658
Joe Frazier!

1436
01:45:33.743 --> 01:45:35.953
<i>- Fight fans, get settled down.</i>
- Go home!

1437
01:45:36.037 --> 01:45:39.162
- Don't stay in the arena!
<i>- It won't be long now.</i>

1438
01:45:40.625 --> 01:45:44.087
<i>Now for the main event.</i>

1439
01:45:47.796 --> 01:45:49.425
<i>On my left</i>

1440
01:45:49.509 --> 01:45:52.636
<i>the challenger, in white trunks,</i>

1441
01:45:52.720 --> 01:45:55.845
<i>weighing 190 pounds.</i>

1442
01:45:55.930 --> 01:45:58.434
<i>Philadelphia's favorite son,</i>

1443
01:45:58.518 --> 01:46:01.354
<i>The Italian Stallion,</i>

1444
01:46:01.435 --> 01:46:03.523
<i>Rocky Balboa.</i>

1445
01:46:10.488 --> 01:46:12.782
<i>And on my right</i>

1446
01:46:12.863 --> 01:46:15.326
<i>wearing red, white and blue,</i>

1447
01:46:15.408 --> 01:46:18.496
<i>weighing 210 pounds,</i>

1448
01:46:18.578 --> 01:46:22.000
<i>undefeated in 46 fights,</i>

1449
01:46:22.332 --> 01:46:24.836
<i>The Master of Disaster,</i>

1450
01:46:25.295 --> 01:46:29.006
<i>the undisputed heavyweight champion</i>
<i>of the world,</i>

1451
01:46:29.090 --> 01:46:30.881
<i>Apollo Creed!</i>

1452
01:46:32.676 --> 01:46:35.220
I want you! You!

1453
01:46:37.930 --> 01:46:40.768
You, chump. I want you!

1454
01:46:40.850 --> 01:46:43.854
You've both fought in Philadelphia before.
You know the rules.

1455
01:46:43.938 --> 01:46:47.064
No low blows,
watch your heads, no butting.

1456
01:46:47.149 --> 01:46:48.899
Shake hands and come out fighting.

1457
01:46:48.984 --> 01:46:50.653
Put your hands up there, chump.

1458
01:46:50.737 --> 01:46:52.863
- Come out fighting.
- Come on!

1459
01:46:54.863 --> 01:46:59.746
<i>Rocky's just going over and being calm,</i>
<i>it looks like from here.</i>

1460
01:47:00.872 --> 01:47:02.787
<i>There goes the big hat.</i>

1461
01:47:06.252 --> 01:47:09.837
<i>I've never seen a fighter</i>
<i>that concerned about his hair.</i>

1462
01:47:17.889 --> 01:47:20.224
<i>There's the bell for round one.</i>

1463
01:47:21.684 --> 01:47:25.813
<i>The fighters come in the center of the ring,</i>
<i>looking at each other.</i>

1464
01:47:25.895 --> 01:47:29.359
<i>Creed, the champion,</i>
<i>zipping in those left-handed jabs.</i>

1465
01:47:29.442 --> 01:47:31.359
<i>Right there. Bang.</i>

1466
01:47:32.987 --> 01:47:36.198
<i>The champ stinging the slower challenger</i>
<i>with jabs at will.</i>

1467
01:47:36.282 --> 01:47:40.243
<i>In fact, it looks like Rocky</i>
<i>is blocking the blows with his face.</i>

1468
01:47:40.328 --> 01:47:44.747
<i>The champion doesn't look the best</i>
<i>he's ever been, but he's moving now.</i>

1469
01:47:44.832 --> 01:47:48.752
<i>The champion's smiling now.</i>
<i>He's toying with him.</i>

1470
01:47:49.587 --> 01:47:52.506
<i>Trying to give the fans</i>
<i>their money's worth.</i>

1471
01:47:54.175 --> 01:47:57.636
<i>He's very clearly outclassed</i>
<i>the challenger right now.</i>

1472
01:47:59.805 --> 01:48:03.768
<i>He's trying to make his man miss like that.</i>

1473
01:48:05.269 --> 01:48:07.895
<i>The champ is just taunting him.</i>

1474
01:48:10.774 --> 01:48:12.609
<i>Creed dancing around.</i>

1475
01:48:14.028 --> 01:48:15.863
<i>I don't believe this!</i>

1476
01:48:15.947 --> 01:48:18.323
<i>The champ is down!</i>

1477
01:48:24.453 --> 01:48:25.662
<i>Creed is down!</i>

1478
01:48:25.747 --> 01:48:27.707
<i>What a surprise this is!</i>

1479
01:48:28.876 --> 01:48:32.212
<i>This is the first time the champion</i>
<i>has ever been knocked down.</i>

1480
01:48:32.296 --> 01:48:34.506
<i>The referee is giving him the count.</i>

1481
01:48:34.590 --> 01:48:37.426
Six, seven, eight.

1482
01:48:37.510 --> 01:48:40.386
<i>He appears to be all right.</i>
<i>Glassy-eyed but okay.</i>

1483
01:48:40.761 --> 01:48:43.972
Go to the ribs! Go to work, Rock!

1484
01:48:44.055 --> 01:48:45.560
Come on!

1485
01:48:46.853 --> 01:48:50.064
<i>Rocky coming back out,</i>
<i>and he's like a bull in a china closet.</i>

1486
01:48:50.148 --> 01:48:53.067
<i>He really wants it. Apollo, left to the head.</i>

1487
01:48:53.192 --> 01:48:56.863
<i>The champion's coming off the floor</i>

1488
01:48:56.944 --> 01:48:59.032
<i>and he's trying to put him away.</i>

1489
01:48:59.113 --> 01:49:00.658
<i>A left, a right.</i>

1490
01:49:00.742 --> 01:49:04.203
<i>Combinations into the face!</i>
<i>That's the Apollo we know.</i>

1491
01:49:08.291 --> 01:49:11.667
<i>Now the champ is taunting Rocky</i>
<i>to come and get some more.</i>

1492
01:49:11.752 --> 01:49:13.377
<i>A left. Another.</i>

1493
01:49:13.880 --> 01:49:15.381
<i>Another left.</i>

1494
01:49:16.841 --> 01:49:18.635
<i>Rocky's coming back!</i>

1495
01:49:20.094 --> 01:49:23.014
<i>Rocky's got him on the ropes!</i>

1496
01:49:23.805 --> 01:49:25.305
Let's break it.

1497
01:49:26.809 --> 01:49:28.353
You're holding.

1498
01:49:28.435 --> 01:49:30.229
You're posing as a boxer.

1499
01:49:30.313 --> 01:49:33.399
<i>There's no way we expected</i>
<i>this kind of hitting.</i>

1500
01:49:36.484 --> 01:49:38.569
Do your best. Do your best.

1501
01:49:40.948 --> 01:49:44.702
<i>Apollo unloading a left.</i>
<i>He's got him up against the ropes.</i>

1502
01:49:52.417 --> 01:49:56.546
<i>They're leading him to his corner.</i>
<i>Rocky can't find his way.</i>

1503
01:49:57.256 --> 01:49:58.631
I called it!

1504
01:49:58.716 --> 01:50:01.260
- Your nose is broke.
- How's it look?

1505
01:50:01.344 --> 01:50:02.845
It's an improvement.

1506
01:50:02.929 --> 01:50:06.180
Quit shucking and jiving! Stick and move!

1507
01:50:06.265 --> 01:50:09.769
Go for the ribs.
Don't let that bastard breathe.

1508
01:50:09.850 --> 01:50:11.270
The guy's quick.

1509
01:50:11.354 --> 01:50:15.149
He doesn't know it's a damn show.
He thinks it's a damn fight.

1510
01:50:15.233 --> 01:50:17.944
Finish this bum, and let's go home.

1511
01:50:18.944 --> 01:50:21.322
Stay to the body. You're doing great!

1512
01:50:21.404 --> 01:50:24.617
<i>Round two.</i>
<i>Creed predicted he'd win in it in three.</i>

1513
01:50:24.701 --> 01:50:28.287
<i>Creed got knocked down in the first.</i>
<i>He came back strong.</i>

1514
01:50:28.621 --> 01:50:30.287
<i>He's working now.</i>

1515
01:50:30.707 --> 01:50:33.457
<i>A sharp left. Again, a hard right.</i>

1516
01:50:33.542 --> 01:50:36.045
<i>Now coming in.</i>
<i>He's knocked him into the corner again.</i>

1517
01:50:36.127 --> 01:50:38.631
<i>The champion's got him</i>
<i>backed into the corner.</i>

1518
01:50:38.715 --> 01:50:42.635
<i>Pummeling him left and right,</i>
<i>his head bouncing against the ropes.</i>

1519
01:50:43.511 --> 01:50:46.595
<i>Balboa's taking</i>
<i>a tremendous beating here.</i>

1520
01:50:46.680 --> 01:50:50.268
<i>Battering him like a punching bag.</i>
<i>What's keeping him up?</i>

1521
01:50:52.603 --> 01:50:54.063
Can't you fight?

1522
01:50:54.145 --> 01:50:57.399
Stop clowning around
and give the people something!

1523
01:50:58.067 --> 01:51:00.403
- Come on!
<i>- He says he wants more!</i>

1524
01:51:00.484 --> 01:51:03.279
<i>He wants more. You folks</i>
<i>watching television around the world</i>

1525
01:51:03.363 --> 01:51:05.408
<i>you're watching a battle.</i>

1526
01:51:10.162 --> 01:51:13.497
<i>Balboa trying to fight back.</i>
<i>Oh, he tagged the champ!</i>

1527
01:51:13.582 --> 01:51:17.086
<i>The champion is trying to get out of there,</i>
<i>but he can't do it.</i>

1528
01:51:17.170 --> 01:51:21.046
<i>He is being barraged with lefts and rights</i>
<i>to the head and body.</i>

1529
01:51:21.131 --> 01:51:24.426
<i>Balboa is tagging the champion</i>
<i>right on the kisser!</i>

1530
01:51:25.426 --> 01:51:28.680
<i>The referee steps in.</i>
<i>They're ready to keep going.</i>

1531
01:51:29.220 --> 01:51:31.059
Back to your corners!

1532
01:51:31.684 --> 01:51:33.603
Come on, Creed!

1533
01:51:34.354 --> 01:51:36.604
<i>This is gonna be a tough one.</i>

1534
01:52:31.243 --> 01:52:33.578
<i>- Back with a left!</i>
<i>- He got tagged!</i>

1535
01:52:35.206 --> 01:52:37.750
<i>The referee's wiping off the gloves.</i>

1536
01:52:42.962 --> 01:52:45.300
<i>Hard left and right combination!</i>

1537
01:52:45.381 --> 01:52:48.301
<i>- What is keeping him up, Bill?</i>
<i>- I don't know.</i>

1538
01:52:50.261 --> 01:52:53.555
<i>He can't even get his gloves up</i>
<i>to protect himself.</i>

1539
01:53:00.979 --> 01:53:03.067
Down! Stay down!

1540
01:53:03.149 --> 01:53:05.444
<i>Apollo has his arms in the air!</i>

1541
01:53:16.497 --> 01:53:17.622
Five.

1542
01:53:18.916 --> 01:53:20.001
Six.

1543
01:53:20.585 --> 01:53:21.792
Seven.

1544
01:53:21.877 --> 01:53:23.046
Eight.

1545
01:53:23.462 --> 01:53:24.546
Nine.

1546
01:53:31.429 --> 01:53:32.680
Come on!

1547
01:53:33.970 --> 01:53:35.975
<i>Apollo can't believe it.</i>

1548
01:53:52.742 --> 01:53:55.953
<i>The champion got a left to his right ribs.</i>

1549
01:53:56.328 --> 01:53:58.537
<i>This has been a tremendous...</i>

1550
01:54:04.337 --> 01:54:05.505
Okay, champ?

1551
01:54:05.587 --> 01:54:06.881
Yeah, I'm okay.

1552
01:54:06.965 --> 01:54:09.591
I may have broke my ribs.

1553
01:54:09.676 --> 01:54:12.136
I can't see nothing. Gotta open my eye.

1554
01:54:12.220 --> 01:54:14.136
- Cut me.
- Don't wanna do it.

1555
01:54:14.220 --> 01:54:16.724
- Go ahead. Cut me.
- Okay.

1556
01:54:16.805 --> 01:54:18.350
Try it. Cut it.

1557
01:54:18.810 --> 01:54:20.685
Creed! Creed!

1558
01:54:22.645 --> 01:54:23.854
Oh, God.

1559
01:54:23.939 --> 01:54:26.734
You're bleeding inside.
I'm gonna stop the fight.

1560
01:54:26.818 --> 01:54:30.113
You ain't stopping nothing, man.

1561
01:54:30.319 --> 01:54:32.782
You stop this fight, I'll kill you!

1562
01:54:34.158 --> 01:54:36.327
- I'm going.
- If you wanna go.

1563
01:54:37.537 --> 01:54:39.872
You gotta give it all!

1564
01:54:39.997 --> 01:54:41.916
You gotta get him!

1565
01:54:47.380 --> 01:54:49.340
<i>The 15th and final round.</i>

1566
01:54:49.421 --> 01:54:52.426
Rocky! Rocky! Rocky!

1567
01:54:58.265 --> 01:55:00.893
<i>They look like they've been in a war.</i>

1568
01:55:08.524 --> 01:55:11.904
<i>A hard right.</i>
<i>The champion really tagged him.</i>

1569
01:55:11.988 --> 01:55:15.948
<i>Apollo clearly protecting</i>
<i>his right side, his ribs.</i>

1570
01:55:19.368 --> 01:55:21.162
<i>Body punches!</i>

1571
01:55:21.247 --> 01:55:24.667
<i>Hard lefts and rights. Look at the blood</i>
<i>coming out of his mouth!</i>

1572
01:55:24.751 --> 01:55:26.877
<i>He's spitting up blood now.</i>

1573
01:55:30.340 --> 01:55:32.841
<i>A tremendous right hand by Rocky.</i>

1574
01:55:32.925 --> 01:55:34.301
Go for it, Rock!

1575
01:55:34.385 --> 01:55:37.430
<i>- Listen to this crowd!</i>
<i>- Right to the ribs.</i>

1576
01:55:37.511 --> 01:55:39.805
<i>Another to the ribs. That left hand again.</i>

1577
01:55:39.890 --> 01:55:43.144
<i>Right to the jaw!</i>
<i>He's got him up against the ropes!</i>

1578
01:55:43.225 --> 01:55:45.313
<i>Apollo the champ...</i>

1579
01:55:48.774 --> 01:55:51.527
Ain't gonna be no rematch.

1580
01:55:52.153 --> 01:55:53.694
Don't want one.

1581
01:56:04.207 --> 01:56:07.167
Rocky, you went the distance, 15 rounds.
How do you feel?

1582
01:56:07.251 --> 01:56:09.752
- All right.
- What were you thinking about...

1583
01:56:09.837 --> 01:56:12.465
- Adrian!
...coming out for the 15th round?

1584
01:56:12.546 --> 01:56:13.800
Adrian!

1585
01:56:15.801 --> 01:56:16.970
Rocky!

1586
01:56:21.305 --> 01:56:23.140
<i>- Tonight...</i>
- Rocky!

1587
01:56:23.225 --> 01:56:26.270
<i>... we have had the privilege of witnessing</i>

1588
01:56:26.354 --> 01:56:29.983
<i>the greatest exhibition of boxing stamina</i>

1589
01:56:30.064 --> 01:56:32.149
<i>in the history of the ring.</i>

1590
01:56:32.234 --> 01:56:33.819
Adrian!

1591
01:56:34.612 --> 01:56:35.822
Rocky!

1592
01:56:36.654 --> 01:56:38.781
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>

1593
01:56:38.864 --> 01:56:41.661
<i>we have a split decision.</i>

1594
01:56:42.868 --> 01:56:44.328
<i>Judge Walker</i>

1595
01:56:47.792 --> 01:56:49.167
<i>for Creed!</i>

1596
01:56:51.837 --> 01:56:53.006
Adrian!

1597
01:56:53.131 --> 01:56:56.634
- Your fans want a rematch.
- Ain't gonna be no rematch!

1598
01:56:58.426 --> 01:57:00.179
- Adrian!
- You heard him...

1599
01:57:00.261 --> 01:57:03.390
- You can't go in there!
- That's my friend. Let go!

1600
01:57:03.474 --> 01:57:05.975
- You're wrecking the jacket!
- Rocky!

1601
01:57:06.060 --> 01:57:08.688
- Paulie.
- Adrian!

1602
01:57:10.398 --> 01:57:12.734
- Adrian! Where's your hat?
- Rocky!

1603
01:57:12.817 --> 01:57:14.068
I love you!

1604
01:57:14.152 --> 01:57:15.528
I love you!

1605
01:57:19.198 --> 01:57:21.701
- I love you!
- I love you!

1606
01:57:21.783 --> 01:57:23.368
I love you!

